{"tid":370670,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 原來林峯都拍過好多武俠小說改編嘅電視劇","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T12:23:28.000Z","uid":34701,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ebf77627b028ab19c4267a48a36082d070aa633","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:04:09.000Z","msg":"睇返wiki佢拍過嘅有：<br />\n黃易三套劇：尋秦記，大唐雙龍傳，覆雨翻雲<br />\n梁羽生嘅雲海玉弓緣，清代女作家陳端生嘅半生緣<br />\n同埋溫瑞安嘅布衣神相，少年四大名捕(而家晏晝重播緊)<br />\n<br />\n咁睇其實林峯真係算好好彩可以拍到咁多套小說名著(你睇古天樂有幸拍到一套尋秦記已經夠佢講到而家，但林峯三套黃易嘅劇都有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n嗰個年代嘅無線都仲係人才鼎盛，就算開劇都未必一定要搵佢啦，可能林峯特別有種古裝味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家睇返少年四大名捕都覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鍾意陳鍵鋒做嘅追命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜而家無線已經好少自家拍小說名著改編嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前嘅好多都真心唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然大部分都改到同原著好唔同，但拍出嚟又有另一種味道，就算重播都會追嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2346c4b2cdfa40a4cba820b0dd486105a63da279","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"除咗金庸嗰啲之外，唔知佢算唔算係拍過最多唔同作家嘅劇呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ab4c818c333dd254b035cf2debe31486810a11","tid":370670,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"仲有布衣神相"},{"pid":"884808dbda930c92d9f0dfc4abb477ab012102ed","tid":370670,"uid":51951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:33:04.000Z","msg":"少年四大有啱啱出道嘅樂瞳睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796c4e9926e31b0976f2dce38d8dfb3e15eff3c9","tid":370670,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"無金庸份"},{"pid":"e7d4a6a926332424041d43d66589ec4b8ee87abc","tid":370670,"uid":51951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無金庸份</blockquote><br />\n00後tvb都冇再拍"},{"pid":"fd787582f904e6ebc2fd8454715227148f2e4480","tid":370670,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"人才鼎盛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64356e2eba277064759976eb223ee33e945e763f","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無金庸份</blockquote><br />\n00後tvb都冇再拍</blockquote><br />\nWiki寫2000年嘅碧血劍都有林峯份，嗰陣佢未出名仲係做茄哩啡角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過之後嗰啲佢拍親都係主要角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295e7b1b63cd5a5d1d995d1696ddd92b456bb620","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人才鼎盛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊01年至08年嗰段時間喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7470e9160ace8d83d434fb435bee73dfb82973","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972612a2d979188ee054a4e37f8d6970c9d9450a","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1667fe98f7f2000a67c0a3e42c35851931d99ce6","tid":370670,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"好好彩?<br />\n知唔知人地老豆乜水"},{"pid":"6b284836748489a43c03b9ab8c1eae75452ef424","tid":370670,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco