lockquote><br />\n仲有佢幫啲古裝劇唱嘅歌都好好聽<br />\n記得忘記<br />\n出鞘<br />\n雙子龍<br />\n領會<br />\n...</blockquote><br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3b7ceef6d52b14d8ffb01e00df09d71ee90a7b","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少年四大有啱啱出道嘅樂瞳睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰陣仲係叫龔茜彤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df759923c658d5c0e8efafdcb137259b6aa2f6e","tid":370670,"uid":102562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"磨劍鋒 來引弓"},{"pid":"3f382fec36101372915541aa8a2c1dc62b3e270b","tid":370670,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>轉個角度佢拍足三套加cctvb力捧先彈得起，古天樂一套已經夠做有凸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實趙盤加大唐都已經夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而唱K keep唔到個勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢拍名捕做冷血都幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唱K係大陸唔係好紅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738b9062a16a0bff3ed880b04563b093e1fafd9d","tid":370670,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇返wiki佢拍過嘅有：<br />\n黃易三套劇：尋秦記，大唐雙龍傳，覆雨翻雲<br />\n梁羽生嘅雲海玉弓緣，清代女作家陳端生嘅半生緣<br />\n同埋溫瑞安嘅布衣神相，少年四大名捕(而家晏晝重播緊)<br />\n<br />\n咁睇其實林峯真係算好好彩可以拍到咁多套小說名著(你睇古天樂有幸拍到一套尋秦記已經夠佢講到而家，但林峯三套黃易嘅劇都有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n嗰個年代嘅無線都仲係人才鼎盛，就算開劇都未必一定要搵佢啦，可能林峯特別有種古裝味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家睇返少年四大名捕都覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鍾意陳鍵鋒做嘅追命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜而家無線已經好少自家拍小說名著改編嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前嘅好多都真心唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然大部分都改到同原著好唔同，但拍出嚟又有另一種味道，就算重播都會追嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家TVB越來越少拍古裝<br />\n一來觀眾口味問題<br />\n二來成本問題 因為可能要拉隊返大陸拍 又要龍虎武師 但點都唔夠大陸鬥<br />\n三來可能係製作能力問題 冇人識寫古裝故事同埋對白 <br />\n睇個勢TVB只會播多D大陸古裝劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094da2a86d7f87619fcb44a7bfe1379eeadf25cd","tid":370670,"uid":87319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"係咪仲有做陸小鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前好似係高清台睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa74cdb4319a02082dee7d4e35d0d96c455a9322","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪仲有做陸小鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前好似係高清台睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陸小鳳係大陸拍嘅，我淨係講咗無線嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果計埋呢套，林峯連古龍都拍埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c0f33688f8159c9c60072d8da49ca38e459979","tid":370670,"uid":61363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"以前TVB就算改名著都有自己味道，碧血劍金蛇郎君無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 封神榜西遊記都改得好有風格"},{"pid":"b4c91cc3a7f0e3c130f6279d6836634cb7bc06a5","tid":370670,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇返wiki佢拍過嘅有：<br />\n黃易三套劇：尋秦記，大唐雙龍傳，覆雨翻雲<br />\n梁羽生嘅雲海玉弓緣，清代女作家陳端生嘅半生緣<br />\n同埋溫瑞安嘅布衣神相，少年四大名捕(而家晏晝重播緊)<br />\n<br />\n咁睇其實林峯真係算好好彩可以拍到咁多套小說名著(你睇古天樂有幸拍到一套尋秦記已經夠佢講到而家，但林峯三套黃易嘅劇都有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n嗰個年代嘅無線都仲係人才鼎盛，就算開劇都未必一定要搵佢啦，可能林峯特別有種古裝味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家睇返少年四大名捕都覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鍾意陳鍵鋒做嘅追命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜而家無線已經好少自家拍小說名著改編嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前嘅好多都真心唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然大部分都改到同原著好唔同，但拍出嚟又有另一種味道，就算重播都會追嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家TVB越來越少拍古裝<br />\n一來觀眾口味問題<br />\n二來成本問題 因為可能要拉隊返大陸拍 又要龍虎武師 但點都唔夠大陸鬥<br />\n三來可能係製作能力問題 冇人識寫古裝故事同埋對白 <br />\n睇個勢TVB只會播多D大陸古裝劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家變咗鍾意玩穿越<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過如果係小說做backup嘅古裝劇都唔會差得去邊嘅，可能成本問題冇再買版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c95c366e92111c2238b6e30c56818866c506a9","tid":370670,"uid":40010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"天    外有天"},{"pid":"3a062189619ddb4789ea3485e5fd3d24daa1b1d3","tid":370670,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"雖然tvb 00年開始已經冇點拍金庸，但林峯係咪氣質唔啱拍金庸？"},{"pid":"bae7cd4e24e7466583bf2389dcd2f8930990a76d","tid":370670,"uid":105428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>事實上佢都拍得好好<br />\n以前都幾多人鍾意睇佢拍古裝</blockquote><br />\n仲有佢幫啲古裝劇唱嘅歌都好好聽<br />\n記得忘記<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">出鞘</span><br />\n雙子龍<br />\n領會<br />\n...</blockquote><br />\n重現世間&quot;毛筆&quot;好兵器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好少人拍古裝有feel<br 